前一講已學到

134
00:08:40.700 --> 00:08:44.990
optional stopping is one way in which you can inflate your Type I error rate.
中停分析是最可能膨脹型一錯誤率的因素

135
00:08:44.990 --> 00:08:48.670
So one thing that you have to do is justify your sample size.
針對這點能做的是明確宣告要收集的樣本數

136
00:08:48.670 --> 00:08:51.280
Of course, thinking about your sample size before you collect
當然事前宣告樣本數也能有效控制型二錯誤率

137
00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:54.840
data is also very useful in controlling your type II error rate.
當然事前宣告樣本數也能有效控制型二錯誤率

138
00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:58.650
Thinking about how many people you need will control both these error rates, but
想清楚要招募多少人能控制兩種錯誤

139
00:08:58.650 --> 00:09:02.980
it will fix the type I error rate to whatever level you've specified.
更能將型一錯誤率固定在設定好的水準

140
00:09:02.980 --> 00:09:05.390
This is sometimes known as the stopping rule.
有時也會遇上必須的中停情況

141
00:09:05.390 --> 00:09:09.960
It can be anything, you can collect data until it starts to rain outside or
像是要在下雨天才能收集資料

142
00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:12.190
until the week is over, anything that you want.
要隔一個星期才能找回受試者等等

143
00:09:13.300 --> 00:09:16.512
In a later lecture, we'll talk about justifying your sample sizes.
之後有一講會談界定樣本數的做法

144
00:09:18.890 --> 00:09:22.611
Another thing you need to specify is the independent variable and
第二點是事先明列統計檢定中的獨變項與依變項

145
00:09:22.611 --> 00:09:26.230
the dependent variable for each test that you want to do.
第二點是事先明列統計檢定中的獨變項與依變項

146
00:09:26.230 --> 00:09:28.880
What is it that you're actually going to analyze?
那些變項是要放進分析程序的？

147
00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:30.780
What are the conditions in your study?
那些變項是標記實驗條件？

148
00:09:30.780 --> 00:09:34.310
And what are the dependent variables with which you measure whatever type of
那些依變項的數值是根據預測所做的測量？

