as you would expect.
主觀預期經由很多方式引導發表的研究結果

199
00:12:34.300 --> 00:12:38.290
The reason for this is that people don't publish their non-significant findings or,
導致出版偏誤的主因是很多人不想發表不顯著的結果

200
00:12:38.290 --> 00:12:41.500
when they are submitted for publication, journals don't accept them.
尤其是很多期刊會拒絕不顯著的結果

201
00:12:42.710 --> 00:12:47.295
Now, this problem is prevented by these registered reports because people say if
註冊報告能避免這樣的問題

202
00:12:47.295 --> 00:12:51.689
you follow this plan, we will publish the results no matter what the outcome.
只要按計畫操作，不管是什麼樣的結果，期刊都會刊出

203
00:12:51.689 --> 00:12:54.963
So this is an important benefit, and if you do a challenging study,
對於挑戰前人的研究，這更是一項優勢

204
00:12:54.963 --> 00:12:58.764
it's very worthwhile to consider following these registered report rules.
值得我們考慮採取註冊研究規範的好處

205
00:13:01.257 --> 00:13:05.100
