像是有些作法不保守、卻更有效率的研究設計

207
00:13:10.770 --> 00:13:13.610
We already discussed how you can improve
前一講提到採用單側檢定能提高檢定力

208
00:13:13.610 --> 00:13:18.540
the statistical power of your test by performing a one-sided test.
前一講提到採用單側檢定能提高檢定力

209
00:13:18.540 --> 00:13:20.750
This also controls the error rate.
這辦法也能控制型一錯誤率

210
00:13:20.750 --> 00:13:24.300
But you're saying that you have a directional prediction.
不過這辦法用在有方向性預測才好

211
00:13:24.300 --> 00:13:25.380
And if this is the case,
如果條件許可

212
00:13:25.380 --> 00:13:28.980
then you can be more efficient in designing a well-powered study.
就能在有高考驗力的研究裡發揮作用

213
00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:33.892
However, people always think that there's something wrong with people who report
只是許多人仍存有成見，
覺得這辦法是用來降低p值的技倆

214
00:13:33.892 --> 00:13:38.149
one-sided tests because it's very often used as a way to reduce the p-value.
只是許多人仍存有成見，
覺得這辦法是用來降低p值的技倆

215
00:13:39.240 --> 00:13:43.790
So in this pre-registered report, you can write down that you have a directional
不過你可以在在註冊報告裡寫清楚方向性假設

216
00:13:43.790 --> 00:13:45.700
prediction, you'll do a one-sided test, and
說明單側檢定的必要性

217
00:13:45.700 --> 00:13:49.340
you can reap the benefits of this directional hypothesis.
就可以用清晰的假設對抗成見

218
