You can see what's required for
根據你的實際需要

221
00:14:02.050 --> 00:14:05.440
you to pre-register your study, which information you need to fill out.
選擇合適的平台預先註冊你的研究

222
00:14:06.590 --> 00:14:09.870
Now, if you do this, you can keep this pre-registration private so
這些平台可以設定不公開預先註冊內容

223
00:14:09.870 --> 00:14:14.040
you don't need to publish it online so that everybody can see what you do.
有需要的話，不必一開始就在網路上完全公開

224
