that you're going to submit your results for publication.
直到正式向期刊投稿為止

226
00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:23.640
And you can say, look, these are the results that I'm presenting, and
你可以昭告天下，剛完成的研究結果

227
00:14:23.640 --> 00:14:28.220
you can see that this is exactly what I predicted when I designed the study.
是完全符合最初設計時的預測

228
00:14:28.220 --> 00:14:29.328
So in this lecture,
簡單總結

